{"tid":1513157,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【逆權運動】閉門會面錄音揭林鄭講大話 拒獨立調查警暴因「警務處同事抗拒好大」","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T19:11:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6231ff7b502efea40645105fafa68ec6d171f535","tid":1513157,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"包括《蘋果日報》在內的多間傳媒日前報道特首林鄭月娥本周一閉門見青年時，透露拒設獨立調查委員會是因為警隊有抗拒，林鄭昨天則在行會前主動「澄清」指政府不設獨立調查委員會與部份警隊人士反對無關，但據《蘋果》取得她前日出席閉門會議時的錄音，可見她雖然沒有直接說明因為這個原因拒設獨立調查委員會，但亦透露警隊有抗拒，不可影響警隊，與傳媒報道意思相近。林鄭當時指：「今日聽起嚟，好多人都話想查警隊濫權，行動有無違反呢樣嗰樣，所以警務處同事對呢樣嘢嘅抗拒好大」，其後她稱近日社會擔心政府會用《基本法》「某些安排」處理香港亂局，所以現時3萬人的警隊對政府尤其重要，「我作為行政長官，係好難係貿然做一啲嘢，係影響佢哋工作嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190828&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59982180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190828%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59982180&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5E%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=fa2aae1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190828%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59982180&h=59c66a0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190828&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59982180</a>"},{"pid":"701db840f6d43dda878d57330e14c8929c085fa8","tid":1513157,"uid":99183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOhUStr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOhUStr.gif&h=ab18dc93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5E%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=55ced040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=